Type: Package
Title: Access The Registry of Research (ROR) API Via R
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Shane Jackson
Maintainer: Shane Jackson <shane.jackson@gmx.co.uk>
Description: An R wrapper for interacting with the Registry of Research API
